Dec 3 (Reuters) - The following financial services industry appointments were announced on Wednesday. To inform us of other job changes, email moves@thomsonreuters.com.

AUSTRALIA AND NEW ZEALAND BANKING GROUP LTD  The company appointed Tracy Ong chief representative, ANZ Malaysia. She joins ANZ from Bank of America Merrill Lynch, Malaysia, where she was most recently managing director, head of corporate banking. [ID:nL3N0TN28V]  MITON GROUP PLC <MGRM.L>  The asset manager appointed Andrew Mellis regional sales manager, effective Jan. 5 next year. [ID:nL3N0TN33M]  ARMSTRONG INVESTMENT MANAGERS  The asset management company appointed Christopher Sullivan director and head of distribution, effective immediately. [ID:nL3N0TN3HK]  AXA ART